        In your neighborhood, city, or town.
      </h2>
      <p>
        Your city or town is likely taking steps to mitigate local emissions. We encourage you to visit your town's website to learn how to get involved. We encourage you to attend a public meeting and contribute your voice.
      </p>

      <h2 class="ui blue header">
        In your region or state.
      </h2>
